com.bigdata.rdf.rio.json

Class SPARQLJSONParserBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openrdf.query.resultio.QueryResultParserBase
      • com.bigdata.rdf.rio.json.SPARQLJSONParserBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.query.resultio.QueryResultParser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BigdataSPARQLResultsJSONParser

    public abstract class SPARQLJSONParserBase
extends org.openrdf.query.resultio.QueryResultParserBase
    Abstract base class for SPARQL Results JSON Parsers. Provides a common implementation of both boolean and tuple parsing.

    Bigdata Changes:

    • Changed the visibility of the method parseValue() from private to protected so we could override it.
    • Pulled some code out of parseQueryResultInternal into its own method so that we can override it.
    Author:
    Peter Ansell, Sebastian Schaffert
